reviewText: I am very pleased with this product.There are 3 CD's with several movies on each.  The majority of them are great and the others are OK but the ones that are great makes it worth the money.  I don't like to swap CD's while I am working so this serves my purpose while entertaining me. Just have to push play between movies.
Title: 10-Movie Mystery Pack
